text: R.K Anand, (born 1 February 1961) is a politician from the Indian state of Manipur. He represented the Naoriya assembly constituency for two terms from 2007-2012 and from 2012-2017. ==References== Category:Indian National Congress politicians Category:Manipur Peoples Party politicians Category:Manipur politicians Category:Living people Category:1961 births Category:People from Imphal
